TEXTUAL NOTES

The text is based on the Lambeth MS. (L) but corrections have been made from the Oxford MS. (O), which is more carefully written, though from Ι. 6. 33, 34 it is to be inferred that it represents the text of the play before it underwent revision for the performance before the King. In a few cases, as will be seen, a correction has been introduced without the authority of O. No notice has been taken in the notes of minor deviations of Ο from L, such as a different order of words. The punctuation given is largely my own.
